Deprecated. As of release 2.5, replaced by de.systemagmbh.tools.util.CSysFlagsVector

public class CSysFlagsVector
extends Vector
implements ISysNamedFlags

CSysFlagsVector is an example for ISysNamedFlags

Example of usage: 

 
                CSysFlagsVector flag=new CSysFlagsVector();
                System.out.println("isSet(test) "+flag.isSet("test"));
                System.out.println("calling set(test) ");
                flag.set("test");
                System.out.println("isSet(test) "+flag.isSet("test"));
                System.out.println("calling set(xxx) ");
                flag.set("xxx");
                System.out.println("isSet(xxx) "+flag.isSet("xxx"));
                System.out.println("calling again: set(xxx) ");
                flag.set("xxx");
                System.out.println("isSet(xxx) "+flag.isSet("xxx"));
                System.out.println("calling revoke(test) ");
                flag.revoke("test");
                System.out.println("isSet(test) "+flag.isSet("test"));
                System.out.println("isSet(xxx) "+flag.isSet("xxx"));
